Sentencas: The flame fuel cell (FFC) is advantageous for its simple setup, quick start-up, and high fuel flexibility.
Titulo: Micro-tubular solid oxide fuel cell stack operated with catalytically enhanced porous media fuel-rich combustor

Sentencas: However, one important drawback of the FFC is its relatively low electrical efficiency, which is mainly limited by the reforming efficiency of the burner and fuel utilization.
Titulo: Micro-tubular solid oxide fuel cell stack operated with catalytically enhanced porous media fuel-rich combustor

Sentencas: In this study, to increase the reforming efficiency and fuel utilization, a catalytically enhanced porous media combustor was integrated with a micro-tubular solid oxide fuel cell stack.
Titulo: Micro-tubular solid oxide fuel cell stack operated with catalytically enhanced porous media fuel-rich combustor

Sentencas: The second layer of the porous material was impregnated with 0.5 wt% Rh, improving the reforming efficiency from 49% to 64.8%.
Titulo: Micro-tubular solid oxide fuel cell stack operated with catalytically enhanced porous media fuel-rich combustor

Sentencas: The fuel utilization was demonstrated to be 32.6% when the equivalence ratio was 1.6 and the inlet flow rate of combustion products to the anode of the stack was 200 mL min(-1).
Titulo: Micro-tubular solid oxide fuel cell stack operated with catalytically enhanced porous media fuel-rich combustor

Sentencas: The effects of the equivalence ratio and anode gas flow rate on the electrochemical performance and efficiency were investigated.
Titulo: Micro-tubular solid oxide fuel cell stack operated with catalytically enhanced porous media fuel-rich combustor

Sentencas: A power density of 72.9 mW cm(-2) and a total electrical efficiency of 12.9% were obtained at a voltage of 0.76 V and an equivalence ratio of 2.4.
Titulo: Micro-tubular solid oxide fuel cell stack operated with catalytically enhanced porous media fuel-rich combustor
